Rest in peace my angel. Thank you for the time you spent with me, for showing me the purest forms of love. For the morning cuddles and kisses, for being my companion, for sitting next to me while I work, and watch tv in bed with me. Thank you for always putting a smile on my face after a long day and for purring next to me whenever you felt I was sad. I will see you in the afterlife my little baby Belz. Always and forever in my heart 💔
How many 👁️ s can you spot? حسد proof 🤣🤣
